# TCP-only stack config (no-UDP hosts / local bridge simulation).
# Copy to deploy/tcp/.env and fill in.

ROOM_PASSWORD=

# SFU keys — must match on the SFU and the relay. Change from the dev defaults.
# The SECRET must be at least 32 characters (LiveKit rejects shorter ones).
LIVEKIT_API_KEY=devkey
LIVEKIT_API_SECRET=change-me-to-a-long-random-secret-32-chars-min

# --- Local simulation (defaults) -------------------------------------------
# Leave these as-is for a local smoke run: the bridge becomes a no-op and the
# stack runs TCP-only on localhost.
# SFU_EXTERNAL_HOST=127.0.0.1
# SFU_EXTERNAL_TCP_PORT=7881
# SFU_LISTEN_TARGET_PORT=7881
# SFU_URL=ws://localhost:7880
# LISTENER_TOKEN_ENDPOINT=http://localhost:8080

# --- Real no-UDP host (single box behind a TLS proxy) ----------------------
# Point SFU_EXTERNAL_* at the host's TCP proxy, and SFU_URL/LISTENER_TOKEN_ENDPOINT
# at the TLS URLs:
# SFU_EXTERNAL_HOST=tcp.your-host.example
# SFU_EXTERNAL_TCP_PORT=30000        # the public port the proxy assigned
# SFU_LISTEN_TARGET_PORT=7881        # the container port the proxy forwards to
# SFU_URL=wss://livekit.your-host.example
# LISTENER_TOKEN_ENDPOINT=https://your-host.example
